{"tid":791002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳警方搜訊滙總部 沈振盈:證券無受影響","createTime":"2018-08-23T12:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T15:11:24.000Z","uid":6604,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce7d36446ea1ac1736ba43c882fa45fbf340bc1","tid":791002,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/7015342/realtime/article/20180823/58598468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2F7015342%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180823%2F58598468&d=8UZu4XPRPMtH7sbCkS5V%2BkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=b92d70a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2F7015342%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180823%2F58598468&h=4eb2b996\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/7015342/realtime/article/20180823/58598468</a><br />\n<br />\n消息人士透露，警方(港島區重案組)昨日到訊滙金融集團位於上環的總部進行搜查，主要針對倫敦金業務，警方帶走了超過十名員工。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，警方今次主要針對集團內的滙凱金業。<br />\n<br />\n據網站資料，訊滙金融成立於1992年，創辦人謝兆凱，旗下包括訊滙證券、訊滙金業、謝氏財務及豐昌投資。滙凱金業則於2009年成立，為香港金銀業貿易場成員。<br />\n<br />\n訊滙證券行政總裁(CEO)沈振盈(沈大師)接受電話查詢時表示，「佢哋(警方)來查金的人」，證券業務並沒有受到影響，他亦不用協助調查。"},{"pid":"63ffc859c5ae731b4f3b57a5f09d271d30af6171","tid":791002,"uid":46933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T12:36:46.000Z","msg":"原來大師做咁多陰質野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ed0fc71e3c44db195fe64463da03e65bae67a5","tid":791002,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T12:38:00.000Z","msg":"師父<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bfbcc1a4794a44f778bb9434f688d677504fb69","tid":791002,"uid":35930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"63ffc859c5ae731b4f3b57a5f09d271d30af6171","tid":791002,"uid":46933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T12:36:46.000Z","msg":"原來大師做咁多陰質野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T12:41:50.000Z","msg":"唔做呢d 靠大師早幾年燈力 早就執笠啦"},{"pid":"a1943ee5e2bb64d1ce9db29600781bac46212807","tid":791002,"uid":169310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:11:24.000Z","msg":"大師間野同殷實商人都係做金起家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本打擊倫敦金係做個樣"}]}